<item>
            <title>[LU-13180] Reserve bit for RDMA-only memory RPC</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13180</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; This is reserved for RDMA-only memory integrated with Lustre.&lt;br/&gt;
  The purpose of this bit is to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  1) disable short IO if memory is not directly addressable from CPU&lt;br/&gt;
  2) prevent CPU memory pages and RDMA memory pages merging into one RPC.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
